contents: Self-Select Plan: Employees choose what doctor and what hospital from a list of approved providers. The premium for the employee is $58 per month and the premium for a family plan (including a spouse and up to 3 children) is $450 per month. The employee pays all medical bills and files a claim form for reimbursement. There is a $1000 deductible for individual plans and a $2500 deductible for family plans.
